Description: High-performance code editor (Devuan/systemd-free build)
 Zed is a modern open-source code editor built in Rust with GPU acceleration.
 .
 This package is built for Devuan Ceres (systemd-free) using elogind/seatd
 for session management. Compiled with x86-64-v3 -O3 optimizations.
 .
 Features: Vulkan renderer, Wayland/X11 support, AI integration, Git, Vim mode.
 .
 Note: Auto-updates disabled; update via APT repository only.
